  <a href="/users/ridethewalrus" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-80357.gif" alt="RideTheWalrus&#039;s picture" title="RideTheWalrus&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>
