    <p>The "internet" as we know it will evolve and adapt into P2P darknets.&nbsp; What we can't do, we code towards.&nbsp; Where we can't get, we route around.&nbsp; What we want to hide, we encrypt.&nbsp; Look for the unintended consequence dupes in government to push for more internet legislation.&nbsp; The end result will be an increase in robustness, privacy and ease of use.</p>

