<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3327944">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Wed, 03/13/2013 - 19:37 | <a href="/news/2013-03-13/guest-post-argentines-escaping-capital-controls-bitcoins#comment-3327944" class="active">3327944</a></span>
