<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3328435">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Wed, 03/13/2013 - 22:49 | <a href="/news/2013-03-13/guest-post-argentines-escaping-capital-controls-bitcoins#comment-3328435" class="active">3328435</a></span>
              <b><a href="/users/labestiol" title="View user profile.">labestiol</a></b>
