</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p>i understand what you are saying.</p>
<p>however, whenever a group of individuals claiming to be the "government" tries to enforce some centrally planned notion of how the economy "ought" to be, that is oppression of the people.</p>
<p>let people decide for themselves what is money, and what is its value.</p>

